        I_HAVE_MY_SUSPICIONS_THAT_YOU_AIDED_THE                               = 7739,  -- I have my suspicions that you aided the thief in his crime, but for the moment I will let that small detail pass. We will see what the villain confesses, however.
        THIS_CAN_T_BE_HAPPENING_I_VE_FAILED                                   = 7740,  -- This can't be happening. I've failed to protect Millechairale...
        SIR_ELMEMAGUE_HAS_TAKEN_THE_SUSPECT_TO_THE                            = 7741,  -- Sir Elmemague has taken the suspect to the chateau for questioning. It's back to regular training drills for us.
        WE_HAVE_RECEIVED_A_REPORT_FROM_SIR_ELMEMAGUE                          = 7742,  -- We have received a report from Sir Elmemague that the suspect we apprehended wasn't the criminal after all. We must be ready to send word to the chateau if any other suspicious characters are sighted.
        THANKS_TO_OUR_EFFECTIVE_TRAINING_DRILLS_WE_WERE                       = 7743,  -- Thanks to our effective training drills, we were able to capture the new suspect with little trouble. Although I do wonder where that other knight disappeared to...
        THE_SUSPECT_APPEARS_TO_HAVE_TAKEN_REFUGE_WITHIN                       = 7744,  -- The suspect appears to have taken refuge within Ordelle's Caves. We will follow our training drills and stick to our posts!
        OUR_RIGOROUS_TRAINING_DRILLS_HAVE_SHOWN_THEIR_WORTH                   = 7745,  -- Our rigorous training drills have shown their worth. That preparation honed the skills we needed to handle the situation this day.
        ANOTHER_SUSPECT_HAS_BEEN_DISCOVERED_IN_ORDELLE_S                      = 7746,  -- Another suspect has been discovered in Ordelle's Caves! We must be ready to move at a moment's notice! Take care to stay out of our way.
        WE_HAVE_SUCCEEDED_NOT_ONCE_BUT_TWICE_AT                               = 7747,  -- We have succeeded not once, but twice at capturing a suspected criminal. I'm certain that this will be the site for developing even more effective training exercises in the future.
        I_HAVE_SPOKEN_WITH_SIR_ELMEMAGUE_NARVECAINT_IS                        = 7748,  -- I have spoken with Sir Elmemague. Narvecaint is currently monitoring the suspect's movements from the entrance to the caves.
        WELL_I_SUPPOSE_WE_CAN_REGARD_THIS_AS                                  = 7749,  -- Well, I suppose we can regard this as an adequate performance. It will still be necessary to further refine our soldiers' training... However, this was an excellent opportunity for the knights to practice their skills in a real-life situation.
        ANOTHER_CHANCE_TO_TEST_THE_EFFECTIVENESS_OF_OUR                       = 7750,  -- Another chance to test the effectiveness of our training in almost exactly the same setting! This time, I expect perfect coordination and execution from my men.
        HMM_THERE_IS_STILL_ROOM_FOR_IMPROVEMENT_THEY                          = 7751,  -- Hmm, there is still room for improvement. They need to work on communication to facilitate speedier responses... Lady Curilla will not be pleased.
        THERE_IS_NOTHING_OUT_OF_THE_ORDINARY_HERE_3                           = 7752,  -- There is nothing out of the ordinary here.
        YOU_CAN_HEAR_A_STRANGE_VOICE_ITEMS_ITEMS                              = 7753,  -- You can hear a strange voice... Items, items, la la la la la`t
        OH_MY_GOB_YOU_RE_ONE_OF_THOSE                                         = 7754,  -- Oh my Gob! You're one of those adventurerurers, aren't ya? You got nothin' on me, man./lady.] I was just mindin' my own businesesess, lookin' for junk an' stuff.
        HEY_WATCH_OUT_YOU_DON_T_WANNA_FIGHT                                   = 7755,  -- Hey, watch out. You don't wanna fight me. I'll turn you into meat jerky! Wait, how about you and me be friends instead? Sound good?
        I_TRAVEL_ALL_OVER_THE_WORLD_AND_HEAR                                  = 7756,  -- I travel all over the world and hear lots of differererent stories. I even hear your stories. I can tell you one, if you want.
