        LISTEN                                                                = 7762,  -- .........listen......
        OH_OUTTA_HERE                                                         = 7763,  -- Oh...... ...outta here.........
        DO_YOU_WANT_TO_HEAR_A_STORY_NO                                        = 7764,  -- Do you want to hear a story? No thank you. Let's hear one(1). Let's hear one(2).
        WHAT_STORY_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_BE_TOLD                                  = 7765,  -- What story would you like to be told? On second thought, maybe later. Dark Puppet. Hitting the Marquisate. I Can Hear a Rainbow. A Timely Visit(pt.1). A Timely Visit(pt.2). The Mothercrystals. The Pursuit of Paradise. Waking the Beast(pt.1). Waking the Beast(pt.2). Chocobo on the Loose! A Goldstruck Gigas(pt.1). A Goldstruck Gigas(pt.2). An Officer and a Pirate. Tenuous Existence. At the Heavens' Door(pt.1). At the Heavens' Door(pt.2). Fate's Call(pt.1). Fate's Call(pt.2). Banishing the Darkness(pt.1). Banishing the Darkness(pt.2). Banishing the Darkness(pt.3). Banishing the Darkness(pt.4). Call of the Void. The Man Behind the Mask. Iroha in Distress(pt.1). Iroha in Distress(pt.2). Iroha in Distress(pt.3). Iroha in Distress(pt.4). The Orb's Radiance. The Silent Forest.
        WHAT_STORY_WOULD_YOU_LIKE_TO_BE_TOLD_2                                = 7766,  -- What story would you like to be told? On second thought, maybe later. Moglesse Oblige(pt.1). Moglesse Oblige(pt.2). Moglesse Oblige(pt.3).
        THE_TELEPOINT_HAS_BEEN_SHATTERED_INTO_A_THOUSAND                      = 7769,  -- The telepoint has been shattered into a thousand pieces...
