        HAVE_YOU_MADE_YOUR_PREPARATIONS                                       = 7771,  -- Have you made your preparations?
        PREPARATIONS_COMPLETE_YES_NOT_YET                                     = 7772,  -- Preparations complete? Yes. Not yet.
        HM_SOMEONE_SEEMS_TO_HAVE_ARRIVED_HERE_BEFORE                          = 7773,  -- Hm...? Someone seems to have arrived here before us.
        STATE_YOUR_REASON_FOR_COMING_HERE                                     = 7774,  -- %, state your reason for coming here.
        YOU_WHAT_ARE_YOU_DOING_HERE                                           = 7775,  -- You! What are you doing here?
        CALM_DOWN_AYAME_HE_S_SHE_S_AN                                         = 7776,  -- Calm down, Ayame. He's/She's] an adventurer. It's his/her] job to go adventuring.
        WE_RE_HERE_TO_INVESTIGATE_SOMETHING_IT_COULD                          = 7777,  -- We're here to investigate something. It could get pretty dangerous, so I suggest taking a few steps back if you know what's good for you.
        WHY_CID_WHAT_BUSINESS_DO_YOU_HAVE_HERE                                = 7778,  -- Why, Cid. What business do you have here today?
        WELL_IF_IT_ISN_T_LITTLE_WOLFGANG_HOW                                  = 7779,  -- Well, if it isn't little Wolfgang. How have you been?
        WE_RE_HERE_TO_CHECK_OUT_THE_CRYSTAL                                   = 7780,  -- We're here to check out the Crystal Line. Recently I've been receiving some very strange readings from this area.
        ACCORDING_TO_THE_DATA_RETRIEVED_BY_A_REPUBLICAN                       = 7781,  -- According to the data retrieved by a Republican party that visited here last month, the once stable energy flow has begun to fluctuate.
        I_VE_NEVER_SEEN_SUCH_HIGH_READINGS                                    = 7782,  -- I've never seen such high readings...
        THE_FLOW_OF_ENERGY_IS_SO_OVERWHELMING_THAT                            = 7783,  -- The flow of energy is so overwhelming that the Telepoint you see over there was shattered to pieces! And now there are reports that a giant beast appeared over the sea, just to the north of Delkfutt's Tower.
        I_HAVE_A_BAD_FEELING_THAT_THESE_TWO                                   = 7784,  -- I have a bad feeling that these two events are connected, and that they're warning us of something worse to come.
        I_UNDERSTAND_THAT_RESEARCH_INCLINES_YOU_TO_PURSUE                     = 7785,  -- ... I understand that research inclines you to pursue these matters. However, I ask that you leave the investigation to the Duchy.
        EH_SO_THE_DUCHY_KNOWS_THE_CAUSE_OF                                    = 7786,  -- Eh? So the Duchy knows the cause of all these strange phenomena?
        NOT_EXACTLY_WE_HAVE_NUMEROUS_PARTIES_INVESTIGATING_THE                = 7787,  -- Not exactly. We have numerous parties investigating the situation. However, many of those sent into the field have...vanished.
        WE_CANNOT_ALLOW_ANY_MORE_ACCIDENTS_THE_DAMAGE                         = 7788,  -- We cannot allow any more accidents. The damage to Vana'diel would be great if we were to lose such an important engineer as you, Cid.
        HAH_LET_ME_GUESS_THE_SCIENTISTS_BACK_IN                               = 7789,  -- Hah! Let me guess... The scientists back in Jeuno told you to get rid of all those who got in their way.
        WHO_DO_THEY_THINK_THEY_ARE_COME_TO                                    = 7790,  -- Who do they think they are!? Come to think of it, I have good reason to believe that it's those lunatics that are causing all this trouble!
        WH_WHAT_IS_GOING_ON                                                   = 7791,  -- Wh-what is going on!?
        A_MOMENT                                                              = 7792,  -- A moment, %!
        COMMON_RUMOR_HAS_IT_THAT_ONE_CAN_MEET                                 = 7793,  -- Common rumor has it that one can meet here with the terrestrial avatar Carbuncle. Could this be true...?
        CARBUNCLE_BRINGER_OF_RAINBOWS_I_AM_TENZEN_OF                          = 7794,  -- Carbuncle, bringer of rainbows! I am Tenzen of the Far East, sent here across the seas at the behest of Phoenix!
        THE_KEEPER_OF_THE_APOCALYPSE_HAS_COME_TO                              = 7795,  -- The Keeper of the Apocalypse has come to Vana'diel, and four of the mothercrystals are besieged by darkness!
        YET_IN_THE_FACE_OF_THIS_CRISIS_BAHAMUT                                = 7796,  -- Yet in the face of this crisis, Bahamut and Diabolos do nothing to defend them.
        DIABOLOS_DRAWS_SOULS_INTO_HIS_DREAMWORLD_TO_SHELTER                   = 7797,  -- Diabolos draws souls into his dreamworld to shelter people from the Emptiness.
        AND_BAHAMUT_RALLIES_HIS_WYRMS_FOR_THE_DESTRUCTION                     = 7798,  -- And Bahamut rallies his wyrms for the destruction of every last person on Vana'diel in the name of some ancient pact!
        CARBUNCLE_WE_ALL_CARRY_THE_CURSE_OF_PROMATHIA                         = 7799,  -- Carbuncle. We all carry the curse of Promathia within us...
        AND_IT_IS_NOT_WITHIN_OUR_POWER_TO                                     = 7800,  -- And it is not within our power to lift this bane...
        BUT_I_CANNOT_ACCEPT_THIS_AS_JUSTIFICATION_FOR                         = 7801,  -- But I cannot accept this as justification for genocide! We were born as a part of fate's design, and we will live the lives we have been given!
        YOU_WHO_HAVE_BROUGHT_THE_SOUL_OF_PHOENIX                              = 7802,  -- You, who have brought the soul of Phoenix across the waves. And you, who carries the blessings of the mothercrystal.
        YOU_HAVE_FINALLY_COME_INTO_CONTACT_WITH_THE                           = 7803,  -- You have finally come into contact with the will of Promathia...
        I_KNEW_THAT_EVEN_SHOULD_THE_PAST_BE                                   = 7804,  -- I knew that even should the past be ground into dust, there would come a time when people would uncover the truth.
        NO_MATTER_HOW_TIGHTLY_SEALED_AS_LONG_AS                               = 7805,  -- No matter how tightly sealed, as long as it exists alongside the mothercrystal, Promathia's will shall one day awaken.
        THAT_IS_WHY_I_HAVE_COME_TO_GUIDE                                      = 7806,  -- That is why I have come to guide you. Guide you to the power of the slumbering gods.
        AS_MANY_PEOPLE_AS_POSSIBLE_MUST_POSSESS_THIS                          = 7807,  -- As many people as possible must possess this strength to prevent the awakening of the Twilight God.
        THE_SLUMBERING_GODS_YOU_SPEAK_OF_THE_GREAT                            = 7808,  -- The slumbering gods... You speak of the great avatars that dream away their existence in every corner of Vana'diel?
        ID_7809                                                               = 7809,  -- ...!?
        I_SENSE_THAT_PHOENIX_DOES_NOT_APPROVE_OF                              = 7810,  -- I sense that Phoenix does not approve of my actions.
        HE_WHO_TRIES_TO_SAVE_THE_WORLD_AND                                    = 7811,  -- He who tries to save the world and he who tries to save mankind... Bahamut and Diabolos would also surely oppose me if they knew of my plans.
        EVERY_TIME_THE_POWER_OF_THE_AVATARS_IS                                = 7812,  -- Every time the power of the avatars is granted to a person, it hastens the awakening of the sleeping gods.
        IF_THE_SIPHONING_OF_ENERGY_CONTINUES_THE_BOUNDARIES                   = 7813,  -- If the siphoning of energy continues, the boundaries of the crystal world they protect will shatter, and their true forms will manifest upon this world of Vana'diel.
        AND_THEN_A_FURIOUS_BATTLE_WILL_ENSUE_BETWEEN                          = 7814,  -- And then a furious battle will ensue between the terrestrial avatars and the newly awakened gods.
        BUT_I_BELIEVE_THAT_THIS_IS_THE_ONLY                                   = 7815,  -- But I believe that this is the only option remaining to prevent Promathia's rebirth.
        THE_AWAKENING_OF_PROMATHIA_DRAWS_NEAR                                 = 7816,  -- The awakening of Promathia draws near.
        WITH_THE_KEEPER_OF_THE_APOCALYPSE_NOW_AMONG                           = 7817,  -- With the Keeper of the Apocalypse now among us, all that remains is for the Gates of Paradise to be opened...
        I_DON_T_UNDERSTAND_HAS_NOT_THE_PURSUIT                                = 7818,  -- I don't understand. Has not the pursuit for the Gates of Paradise all been the result of Promathia's curse?
        IF_SO_THEN_EVERYTHING_HAS_BEEN_FOR_THE                                = 7819,  -- If so, then everything has been for the purpose of awakening the Twilight God...
        CARBUNCLE_DESTROYING_HIS_MINION_OURSELVES_IS_THE_ONLY                 = 7820,  -- Carbuncle! Destroying his minion ourselves is the only way to save the children of Altana!
        I_BEG_OF_YOU_TO_LEND_US_THE                                           = 7821,  -- I beg of you to lend us the strength we need! Please tell us where to find the Keeper of the Apocalypse!
        YOU_SHINE_SO_BRILLIANTLY_I_KNOW_THAT_GUIDING                          = 7822,  -- You shine so brilliantly... I know that guiding light well.
        IT_IS_THE_LIGHT_STANDING_AT_YOUR_SIDE                                 = 7823,  -- It is the light standing at your side, merging with your own, that so fills you with hope.
        VERY_WELL_I_WILL_GRANT_YOU_MY_ASSISTANCE                              = 7824,  -- Very well. I will grant you my assistance.
        YOU_WILL_HELP_US                                                      = 7825,  -- You will help us!?
        THIRTY_YEARS_AGO_I_SENSED_THE_BIRTH_OF                                = 7826,  -- Thirty years ago, I sensed the birth of the Keeper of the Apocalypse.
        AFTER_A_NUMBER_OF_YEARS_THE_PRESENCE_FADED                            = 7827,  -- After a number of years the presence faded, and I can no longer sense its location.
        HOWEVER_THE_FIERY_BIRD_OF_RESURRECTION_WILL_CONTINUE                  = 7828,  -- However, the fiery bird of resurrection will continue to lead your steps on this journey.
        AND_THAT_IS_WHY_I_WILL_LEND_MY                                        = 7829,  -- And that is why I will lend my strength to Phoenix's diminished soul...
        YOU_HAVE_OUR_THANKS_BRINGER_OF_RAINBOWS_I                             = 7830,  -- You have our thanks! Bringer of rainbows, I am delirious with joy at your words!
        DO_NOT_REJOICE_JUST_YET_TENZEN_THE_ENERGY                             = 7831,  -- Do not rejoice just yet, Tenzen. The energy I will share with Phoenix does not exist here.
        IT_CAN_BE_FOUND_IN_THE_CITY_BUILT                                     = 7832,  -- It can be found in the city built by the Kuluu on the outskirts of the Zilartian capital. A place known as Pso'Xja.
        THE_POWER_WE_GRANTED_THE_KULUU_IN_ANCIENT                             = 7833,  -- The power we granted the Kuluu in ancient times should still be sealed within that city.
