        THIS_CHOCOBO_RIDING_IS_A_LOT_MORE_PAINFUL                             = 7847,  -- This chocobo riding is a lot more painful than it looks. I think I'm starting to chafe.
        I_WONDER_HOW_MUCH_I_COULD_GET_FOR                                     = 7848,  -- I wonder how much I could get for this at the local pawnshop...
        WOULD_SOMEBODY_EXPLAIN_TO_ME_WHY_WE_RE                                = 7849,  -- Would somebody explain to me why we're collecting these things again?
        DIGGING_HOLES_IN_THE_DIRT_YEAH_THIS_IS                                = 7850,  -- Digging holes in the dirt... Yeah, this is my idea of excitement.
        DIGS_UP_STRANGE_TRADING_AND_PLACES_IN_THE                             = 7851,  -- % digs up # strange trading [card/cards] and places [it/them] in the treasure pool.
        VANA_DIEL_IS_UNDER_ATTACK_BY_VILLAINS_IN                              = 7852,  -- Vana'diel is under attack by villains in samurai armor! Help the moogles in each nation defeat this menace, kupo!
        WE_VE_MIXED_UP_SOME_MOOGLE_MAGIC_TO                                   = 7853,  -- We've mixed up some moogle magic to crack that aura, but you'll need to equip a special weapon to even cause a scratch, kupo!
        TH_THAT_IT_MAY_BE_JUST_THE_THING                                      = 7854,  -- Th-that %... It may be just the thing for whacking those wacky samurai! Hold still while I work my moogle magic, kupo!
        YOU_WON_T_BE_ABLE_TO_HURT_THOSE                                       = 7855,  -- You won't be able to hurt those harbingers of harm with %. You must equip the %, kupo!
        I_CAN_T_WORK_MY_MOOGLE_MAGIC_WHILE                                    = 7856,  -- I can't work my moogle magic while you're involved in other events, kupo!
        TIME_ELAPSED_VANA_DIEL_TIME_AND_EARTH_TIME                            = 7857,  -- Time elapsed: # [hour/hours] (Vana'diel time) # [minute/minutes] and # [second/seconds] (Earth time)
        WHILE_I_M_SURE_YOU_ARE_IN_THE                                         = 7858,  -- %. While I'm sure you are in the middle of some important mission, could you spare a few moments for me?
        YOU_KNOW_ABOUT_THE_SLEEPING_GODS_THE_AVATARS                          = 7859,  -- You know about the sleeping gods...the avatars that guard the protocrystals?
        I_AM_AS_DIFFERENT_TO_THOSE_BEINGS_AS                                  = 7860,  -- I am as different to those beings as fire is to water, and yet we share the same desire to protect Vana'diel.
        THAT_IS_WHY_I_AIDED_THE_BLOSSOMING_OF                                 = 7861,  -- That is why I aided the blossoming of their power within you and your fellow adventurers.
        I_BELIEVED_THAT_IF_THEIR_ASPECTS_FOUGHT_BESIDE                        = 7862,  -- I believed that if their aspects fought beside you, they would learn from an existence that had lost the gift of eternity.
        FINALLY_THE_SLEEPING_GODS_BEGIN_TO_STIR_FROM                          = 7863,  -- Finally, the sleeping gods begin to stir from their slumber.
        WILL_THEY_CONSENT_TO_JOIN_US_IN_OUR                                   = 7864,  -- Will they consent to join us in our roles as guardians of Vana'diel?
        I_HOPE_TO_ASK_THIS_VERY_QUESTION_TO                                   = 7865,  -- I hope to ask this very question to an old friend of mine who resides at the Full Moon Fountain. A very, very old friend...
        BUT_IN_ORDER_TO_WAKE_HIM_I_NEED                                       = 7866,  -- But in order to wake him, I need a vast source of energy.
        I_HOPE_TO_VISIT_THE_FULL_MOON_FOUNTAIN                                = 7867,  -- I hope to visit the Full Moon Fountain, and ask the sleeping Fenrir to see what the future holds.
        BUT_IN_ORDER_TO_WAKE_HIM_FROM_HIS                                     = 7868,  -- But in order to wake him from his weakened torpor, I need an energy source of immense proportions.
        THAT_IS_WHERE_YOU_COME_IN_IF_YOU                                      = 7869,  -- That is where you come in. If you could gather the power of the sleeping gods and bring it to the Full Moon Fountain, we might have a chance.
        IF_YOU_USE_THIS_TO_ENTER_THE_PROTOCRYSTALS                            = 7870,  -- If you use this % to enter the protocrystals, you will be closer to the true avatars than anyone has ever been before. But be warned: the ensuing battle will be that much more difficult.
        YOU_AND_YOUR_FELLOW_ADVENTURERS_ARE_THE_ONLY                          = 7871,  -- You and your fellow adventurers are the only ones capable of besting the six sleeping gods and tapping the elemental energy that they wield.
        I_SET_THIS_TASK_BEFORE_YOU_THERE_IS                                   = 7872,  -- I set this task before you, %. There is little time to waste...
        GATHER_THE_ELEMENTAL_ENERGY_FROM_THE_SIX_SLEEPING                     = 7873,  -- Gather the elemental energy from the six sleeping gods and make your way to the Full Moon Fountain...
        THEN_WE_SHALL_SEE_IF_MY_ANCIENT_FRIEND                                = 7874,  -- Then we shall see if my ancient friend can be roused...
        THANK_YOU_FOR_BRINGING_THE_SHELL_OF_MY                                = 7875,  -- Thank you for bringing the shell of my avatar, %.
        I_THOUGHT_THAT_YOU_WOULD_NEVER_RETURN_TO                              = 7876,  -- I thought that you would never return to this place. I threatened your life, even if it was for the purpose of defeating the sleeping gods.
        BUT_YOU_FOUGHT_ME_WITH_EVERY_OUNCE_OF                                 = 7877,  -- But you fought me with every ounce of your strength, and bent the power of those slumbering deities to your will.
        THAT_IS_WHAT_SAVED_US_AT_THE_END                                      = 7878,  -- That is what saved us at the end.
        UNFORTUNATELY_IT_DID_NOT_HAVE_THE_DESIRED_EFFECT                      = 7879,  -- Unfortunately, it did not have the desired effect...
        YOU_WERE_NEVER_MEANT_TO_SUBMIT_TO_THE                                 = 7880,  -- You were never meant to submit to the will of the sleeping gods. And I will never lose my faith in the children of Vana'diel.
        EVEN_THOSE_ANCIENT_BEINGS_WILL_ONE_DAY_LEARN                          = 7881,  -- Even those ancient beings will one day learn a great truth from mortals.
        SO_I_WANT_FOR_YOU_TO_HAVE_THIS                                        = 7882,  -- So I want for you to have this. Lend me your strength again, %. We will succeed in waking my old friend.
        I_HAVE_NEED_OF_YOUR_HELP                                              = 7883,  -- %. I have need of your help.
        MY_OLD_FRIEND_AT_THE_FULL_MOON_FOUNTAIN                               = 7884,  -- My old friend at the Full Moon Fountain calls for me.
